tags: get your cameras OUT OF HERE
JUST LET HER LIVE HER LIFE
summary: just saw an article complaining about how taylor used an umbrella to conceal herself from a camera while getting off a plane in...
body: just saw an article complaining about how taylor used an umbrella to conceal herself from a camera while getting off a plane in australia and i’m so fired about this. its not her responsibility to smile into your camera when she’s getting off of a private plane. especially after she has made it abundantly clear that she does.not.want.to.be.in.the.public.eye.that.way. when will these stupid entertainment journalists and paps get it through their thick skulls that this is a clear invasion of privacy and that taylor does not owe them anything. not public appearances, not posing for paparazzi pictures, not answering their shallow, brainless questions about her personal life. not ANYTHING. let her get off her plane, go to lunch, walk from her apartment to her car, do everything that everyone else gets to do un-violated, without shoving a camera in her face. she’s a human freaking being, not an animal in a zoo. (though taylor swift is technically also the name of a certain animal in a certain zoo, but you know what i mean.)
